				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Ok, that 10 save verussu magic helps, to the person who asked, with this.<BR>
<BR>
It will not affect fire based spells, or cold based spells (most wizards get both, druids and mage get fire, shaman get cold). the SV magic helps with spells like lighting (anotehr wiz and druid spell) cleirc strike series, root, etc. It might also help agaisn Charm, but it is also believe that your Charisma affects that, unsure about that one. The wizards in Mistmoor like to Force Strike a lot, and with 68  magic resistance, I resist a lot of them. this istem cna be a life saver.
				</font>
			</td>

	</tr>
	
